snippet.title: Official Dub Dash Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer of Dub Dash, a fast-paced rhythm game based on breathtaking electronic music. Dub Dash features an eye-catching 360° spherical rendering style, and 7 impressive gameplay mechanics with a catchy, yet ultra challenging gameplay. Music in the trailer by Bossfight!

Play now on iOS: http://play.DubDashGame.com
Release on Android and Steam: February 16th 2016

Official Website: http://www.DubDashGame.com
Official Blog: http://www.incodra.com/blog
TouchArcade: http://forums.toucharcade.com/showthread.php?t=272644

Follow us on:
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/c/DubDashGame
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/DubDashGame
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/DubDashGame
